      "content": "but that's the thing... i don't want to \"allow\" it or \"heal.\" that just sounds like more work. i'm just done. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen so i don't have to deal with this anymore. it would just be easier if i didn't have to wake up to this every single morning.",
